                                 Map & Directions


                                [laMap.gif]
       DIRECTION : From the 605 S exit Katella Ave (only exits in one
    direction) travel about 2 miles and Los Alamitos will be on your left
   hand side...From the 22 Highway North (to Long Beach) exit Valley View
   travel north about 4 miles then make a left on Katella Ave. Race track
                will be on your immediate right hand side.

